title: MAC OS Templates for MS Office & Adobe Photoshop & Excel
description:
System Requirements
* Mac OS Leopard 10.5 or newer including Mavericks
* Photoshop CS3, CS4, CS5, CS6 or Creative Cloud supports both 32 bit and 64 bit 
* Photoshop Elements 8,9,10,11
* Lightroom 2.7 or newer 
* 4 GB RAM or more
 Languages : English, French, Deutsch, Português Brasileiro
